  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>State Gauss&#8217;s law</item>
<item>Explain the conditions under which Gauss&#8217;s law may be used</item>
<item>Apply Gauss&#8217;s law in appropriate systems</item></list></md:abstract>
